果真係假消息 咁你拉個女仔未呀？<br />\n屌你老母嬲撚到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:06:00.000Z","msg":"PK Tang<br />\n<br />\n1. 真假既都拎上庭囉,還你清白呀嘛<br />\n2. 咁大間警署有cctv 證明你清白?以後不如搵賭場保安公司幫警署裝cctv,保證360度冇死角24小時錄影。Server 放係法庭，有人告就去搵法庭既人review ，一定可以避免警察比人誣告。<br />\n<br />\n3. 點解我要信你話係假就係假?有冇證據?人地話你警暴有片有人證，而家叫你去查你唔去查仲要問人拎證據?口供唔係證據?你唔查可以，9月立法會有半數位既你等睇四年冇糧出啦。"},{"pid":"fdc99de039fc4c232f62077f789cd84f1ce19566","tid":1834092,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d17622e3fc644dfebae31329ffd42f076f6f5f88","tid":1834092,"uid":207614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cb0257a5bbe90e0e8362db191ebca46c4c5a729","tid":1834092,"uid":40520,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"香港自稱好黃既醫護：有需要會出聲<br />\n到被人反告都冇需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"保護病人<br />\n放過黑警<br />\n開個記者會都已經夠大聲 又唔洗開名<br />\n另外就係 就咁濫捕傷個D都已經可以開個大既記者會逐單數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"班連登醫護狗又會屌你分化撚<br />\n奇在佢地同777 popo一樣<br />\n一句都駁唔到就屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1538e1233d3397db98f4fb0f70b55ed78d4278","tid":1834092,"uid":41849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E6%25A1%2588&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=2bb67d9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E6%A1%88</a><br />\n<br />\n以前真實發生過<br />\n有一必有二三四<br />\n點會一定冇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f6f70171cfd100b9ed8390e8f5a8faa1126a2a","tid":1834092,"uid":212944,"l